title: 2 bed / 1 bath - Lower Unit of Duplex
posting_body: ['Fantastic location!', 'This location sits in the popular Merriam Park neighborhood, which has all the essential destinations within a 10 minute walk.', 'There are several colleges including Concordia, Macalester, St. Thomas, St. Kates, and Hamline.', 'Allianz Field, Target, Whole Foods, and Cub along with the light rail makes this a superb spot.', 'Enjoy this 2 bed 1 bath featuring in unit washer and dryer, a fully renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, hardwood flooring/vinyl, deck area and garage parking.', 'There is a fenced in backyard.', 'Pets are welcome for a $350 non-refundable deposit in addition to a $50 monthly charge.', 'Flat rate $150 for utilities (gas, electric, water, trash).', 'Tenants responsible for cable/internet.', 'Garage parking spot available for $50/month.', 'Driveway spots and street parking available as well.', 'MINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS:', '-No smoking', '-No prior evictions', '-Gross monthly income must be 3x the rent', '-Credit score of at least 620', '-No criminal background']
